fields.text:
Creative acts propel me through each day. During my days at university, I inhabited creative studios, classrooms and offices. I learned and earned. After many epiphanies, conversations and inspiration from incredible people, I now inhabit new spaces. I find myself in gardens, in kitchens and in communities.

I am an Oregonian looking to bring my creative skills into the realm of solutions. I enjoy collaborating with non-profits, organizers and those working for change.
